reviews.course_name: Gen Chem Lab and Orgo Lab
reviews.review_content: I disagree with the above reviewer.  Jebejian is the best!!  I had her for g-chem and quant lab.  Although she is pretty strict come to lab prepared and you should not have a problem.  She is a little old fashion in her methods but she means well.
